race.description: Ballina Rsl *Big Dance Eligibility* Ballina Cup
race.comment: TRIBECA STAR (4) made significant improvement at his second run back when a slashing third over 1400m at Eagle Farm in a C6. Steps out to this trip for the first time and gets every chance from the gate. HURSTVILLE ZAGREB (5) frustrating Sydney-trained gelding who can take control early in this weaker race. Set a decent tempo before fading when fourth over 1600m at Randwick. Leading jockey booked and has genuine top-three prospects. PERFECT PLAY (3) model of consistency this campaign and has the ability to overcome the awkward gate. Kept coming through the line when second to Zaphod over 1825m at Eagle Farm in C6 grade. Proven at the trip and comes here in peak condition. HADOUKEN (6) has needed the two runs for the new yard, and he gets a much better setup today. Knocked up late with the 61.5kg when seventh over 1550m at Murwillumbah. Stays in the calculations.
